sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant OnlineFS as Online Feature Server<br/>6566/TCP HTTP or 6567/TCP HTTPS
    participant Redis as Redis/PostgreSQL<br/>6379/TCP or 5432/TCP
    participant Registry as Registry Server<br/>6570/TCP gRPC
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over MLApp,OIDC: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval (Real-time Inference)

    MLApp->>OnlineFS: POST /get-online-features<br/>Bearer Token (optional)<br/>gRPC or HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)

    alt Authentication Enabled
        OnlineFS->>OIDC: Validate JWT Token<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDC-->>OnlineFS: Token Valid
    end

    OnlineFS->>Registry: GetFeatureView<br/>gRPC/6570<br/>Fetch metadata
    Registry-->>OnlineFS: Feature metadata

    OnlineFS->>Redis: GET features<br/>Redis Protocol or PostgreSQL
    Redis-->>OnlineFS: Feature values

    OnlineFS-->>MLApp: JSON/Protobuf Response<br/>Feature values

    Note over MLApp,OIDC: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Training)

    participant Training as Training Job
    participant OfflineFS as Offline Feature Server<br/>8815/TCP HTTP or 8816/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Training->>OfflineFS: POST /get-historical-features<br/>Bearer Token (optional)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    alt Authentication Enabled
        OfflineFS->>OIDC: Validate JWT Token<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDC-->>OfflineFS: Token Valid
    end

    OfflineFS->>Registry: GetFeatureView<br/>gRPC/6570<br/>Fetch metadata
    Registry-->>OfflineFS: Feature metadata

    OfflineFS->>S3: GET offline features<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>OfflineFS: Feature data (Parquet/CSV)

    OfflineFS-->>Training: Historical features<br/>Point-in-time correct

    Note over MLApp,OIDC: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Offline to Online)

    participant CronJob as CronJob

    CronJob->>OnlineFS: POST /materialize<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    OnlineFS->>OfflineFS: GET historical features<br/>HTTP/8815 or HTTPS/8816
    OfflineFS->>S3: Fetch offline data<br/>HTTPS/443
    S3-->>OfflineFS: Feature data
    OfflineFS-->>OnlineFS: Feature values

    OnlineFS->>Redis: WRITE features<br/>Redis Protocol/6379 or PostgreSQL/5432<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    Redis-->>OnlineFS: Write confirmed

    OnlineFS-->>CronJob: Materialization complete

    Note over MLApp,OIDC: Flow 4: Feature Registry Management

    participant CLI as feast CLI/SDK
    participant RegDB as Registry DB<br/>PostgreSQL/S3/SQLite

    CLI->>Registry: ApplyFeatureView<br/>gRPC/6570 or 6571<br/>Bearer Token (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)

    alt Authentication Enabled
        Registry->>OIDC: Validate JWT Token
        OIDC-->>Registry: Token Valid
    end

    Registry->>RegDB: Store feature definition<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 or S3/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    RegDB-->>Registry: Stored

    Registry-->>CLI: FeatureView created
